@page "/menu"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Menu</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md mt-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-700 mb-6 border-b pb-2">Our Menu</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        <p>
            Our current menu features a premium selection of butcher-block staples and specialty items tailored for every palate. Our signature beef offerings include thick-cut ribeyes, tender New York strips, and perfectly lean ground chuck blends ideal for making the ultimate juicy burgers at home. Each beef cut is aged to perfection to guarantee an incredibly rich flavor profile.
        </p>
        <p>
            For those looking beyond beef, we offer an array of exceptional pork and poultry options. Choose from thick, center-cut pork chops, tender baby back ribs ready for the smoker, and all-natural chicken breasts or drumsticks. Our artisan deli section also highlights small-batch, hardwood-smoked bacon and traditional German-style bratwursts made fresh in-house every morning.
        </p>
        <p>
            All items listed are available by the pound or in curated bundle packs designed to give you the best value for your weekly meal prep. Select your favorite cuts below, customize your order package, and proceed to our streamlined checkout. Please note that availability may vary daily based on what our local farming partners deliver each morning.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Choose</h2>
            <p class="text-muted fs-5">What will it be...</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <img src="images/ribs.jpg"
                     class="card-img-top img-fluid multi-img"
                     alt="Ribs Delish" />
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title fw-semibold mb-0">Ribs</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <img src="images/burger.jpg"
                     class="card-img-top img-fluid multi-img"
                     alt="Burger Yum" />
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title fw-semibold mb-0">Hamburger</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <img src="images/sashimi.avif"
                     class="card-img-top img-fluid multi-img"
                     alt="Something Fishy" />
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title fw-semibold mb-0">Fish</h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


